This basic game has a 800 by 600 set resolution, but will be updated for in the future. 
--------
The bullets are set ready to fire whenever you decide to hit the space bar and it 
will travel until it reaches the end of the screen or if it hits an enemy.
--------
You can change the number of enemy aliens with the 'num_of_enem' variable.
So far, it is set to 15 enemies and the game won't end until the aliens reach your ship.
